  "detailed_description": "The robots are trying to take over!<br><br><strong><u>Features</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246710/extras/c7699bbeb2327fdd46985f10006ee93e.avif?t=1705185808\" width=495 height=120 /></span><br><strong>Heroes</strong><br>Unlock and play as different heroes, each with their own distinct abilities and playstyles that help slay all the bots in sight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246710/extras/78c859b24ab3cacbab546427e7cb8175.avif?t=1705185808\" width=80 height=120 /></span>         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246710/extras/13e1d4a01ba36a9f9ae627c1d631c0ae.avif?t=1705185808\" width=80 height=120 /></span>         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246710/extras/03ac5f0303a7d2f6ae2dce52a357f16f.avif?t=1705185808\" width=80 height=120 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246710/extras/29321f6739844e8430a6a10730116014.avif?t=1705185808\" width=80 height=120 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246710/extras/14f4057f2209741be1e530192fb8a80d.avif?t=1705185808\" width=80 height=120 /></span><br><br><strong>Items</strong><br>Acquire items from vending machines to boost your robot dismantling potential. Unlock new items by completing various achievements.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246710/extras/c5766b2dc047df3accbb397c9ad397d1.apng?t=1705185808\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246710/extras/c5766b2dc047df3accbb397c9ad397d1.poster.avif?t=1705185808\" class=\"bb_img\" width=215 height=140 /></picture></span><br><br><strong>Enemies</strong><br>Face off against the robot army! Watch out as they tend to overwhelm anyone in their path.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246710/extras/fb82a0572e67cb93bf97c7852668a539.apng?t=1705185808\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246710/extras/fb82a0572e67cb93bf97c7852668a539.poster.avif?t=1705185808\" class=\"bb_img\" width=185 height=125 /></picture></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246710/extras/c12b75ac12f29a32e6368404ac564446.avif?t=1705185808\" width=216 height=183 /></span><br><br><strong>Bosses</strong><br>Face the leaders of the robot army head on by surviving and destroying all the bots before.<br><br><strong>Locations</strong><br>Travel to different locations and stop the robots and their evil plan. Fight your way through the relentless rounds of robots, defeat the boss and escape, or continue to see how long you can survive.<br><br><strong>Become Powerful</strong><br>Level up and unlock all the Cybernetic Enhancements and become the ultimate robot killing machine.",
